rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0001
rows.name: The Central Life is here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0002
rows.name:
The coordinates point to the ocean
west of the Black Steel Continent.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0003
rows.name:
It seems it is submerged underwater.
That explains why it hadn't been found until now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0004
rows.name: It's at the bottom of the sea-meh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0005
rows.name:
Even if it is on the ocean floor,
we have to go.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0005_02
rows.name: Right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0006
rows.name: The survival of humanity depends on your work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0007
rows.name: Elma, please save us. I beg you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0008
rows.name: Stop acting like a stranger, Nagi.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0009
rows.name:
I boarded your ship for that very purpose,
and now I am here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0010
rows.name:
My determination hasn't changed a bit
since back then.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0011
rows.name:
I'm sorry.
Always relying on you like this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0012
rows.name:
In exchange, once everything is resolved,
give me a long vacation.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0013
rows.name:
This planet is endlessly interesting.
There are many places I want to visit regardless of missions.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0014
rows.name: In that case, Tatsu will guide you-meh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0015
rows.name:
Ah, of course, no payment needed-meh.
Free of charge is fine-meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0016
rows.name: Honestly Tatsu, where did you learn a word like that?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0017
rows.name:
We've already transmitted the Central Life's coordinates
to each team.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0018
rows.name:
Elma, I want you to take
frontline command of all teams.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0019
rows.name: I humbly accept, Chief Engineer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0020
rows.name: As I thought, that title feels more right![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0021
rows.name: "Commander" and such is too stiff and stuffy for me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0022
rows.name: I figured as much.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0022_2
rows.name: Well then, everyone, let's go![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0023
rows.name: Yes![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12030100_MSG0024
rows.name: I brought the bento too-meh![ST:wait ]
